dct_title_s: Multiple Species Habitat Conservation Plan (MSHCP) Boundaries, Riverside County California, 2019
dct_description_sm: This is the boundary layer of the Mulit-Species Habitat Conservation Plan (MSHCP). Western MSHCP boundary also used for Western MSHCP Open Space Fee Area. Per Ord. 810, Sec 8.Section 8. Western Riverside County Multiple Species Habitat Conservation Plan Fee Area Boundary. The boundary of the Western Riverside County Multiple Species Habitat Conservation Plan Fee Area is the same as the MSHCP boundary as set forth in that document entitled MSHCP Plan Area Map dated June 2003, which is on file with the Clerk of the Board.
